<br>
Yesterday was just plain annoying.. almost back to 38 (after having lost it to a combination of Rygorr oracle and elite and snow griffon)... hunting a little snow cougar in eastern wastes.... an elder snow griffon runs past, proceeds to attack. I SNARE it.. YAY! Start running at low health... and spirit of wolf drops... did I mention the cougar also found a dire wolf friend?  *crunch*<br>
<br>
So I retrieve my belongings, and me and Meledi hunt a bit further back, me pulling things (to reduce our danger).  All is happy for a while, I&quot;m looking at 38 again... and fear lasts really long on that tundra kodiak and it runs into the path of that elder snow griffon again...  I try to snare.. resist... *crunch*<br>
<br>
Hrmph... <br>
<br>
/gu *whines* Cleric around for pile of bodies on the dragon bridge?<br>
*drags corpses into a &quot;Y&quot; for &quot;Yell&quot; at the suggestion of Meledi*<br>
*debates on whether to drag corpse over from Rygorr Fort to start next letter*<br>
<br>
Blayze, sweetheart that he is, comes and rezzes me and Meledi (she actually made it within reach of the zone before succumbing).   So we are sitting on the dragon bridge (usually out of range of normal mobs), recuperating (Hey, I'm close to 38 again!) .. and what do I see?  Yep, you guessed it.<br>
<br>
Did I mention I had sowed Blayze and Meledi, but not myself (yet)  ...?<br>
<br>
/sigh<br>
<br>
Thankfully snare stuck this time, and I crawled my way to the zone =P<br>
<br>
Those guys WILL pay someday.<br>
